## Description {#details}

Errors of this type should be returned if a module contains definitions for symbols that are not claimed by the module&#39;s associated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/materializationresponsibility">MaterializationResponsibility</a>.

If this error is returned it is indicative of a broken transformation / compiler / object cache.

Definition at line 538 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/executionengine/include/llvm/executionengine/orc/core-h">Core.h</a>.
